### AI MODERATION (Admin only)
### ============================================================

### TC-COMP-36: Run AI moderation on a complaint
POST {{baseUrl}}/complaints/moderate
Authorization: Bearer {{orgAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "complaintId": "{{complaintId}}"
}

